pageProduct.name: Skin Republic Collagen Hydrogel Face Mask
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Hydrogel facial sheet mask infused with Collagen for instantly hydrated, younger looking skin.

  • Instant hydration
  • Nutrient rich serum helps nourish skin
  • Reduces the visible signs of aging

Super-hydrating Hydrogel serum sheet mask instantly reveals a radiant, glowing complexion. Nutrient packed Sea Minerals nourish and hydrate. Collagen and Argan Oil help reduce the visible signs of aging. Skin appears smooth, plump and more youthful.

Ingredients

qua, Butylene Glycol, Glycerin, Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) Fruit Extract, Mineral Oil, Ceratonia Siliqua Gum, Chondrus Crispus (Carrageenan), Cellulose Gum, Sodium Polyacrylate, Hydrogenated Polydecene, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Hydrolyzed Collagen, Polysorbate 20, Laminaria Japonica Extract, Salicornia Herbacea Extract, Algae Extract, Gelidium Cartilagineum Extract, Trideceth-6, Sodium Hyaluronate, Disodium EDTA, Phenoxyethanol, CI 42090, Parfum.

Directions

Cleanse skin, remove mask from packaging. There are two sections of the mask. Remove thin tissue backing from mask and discard. Place hydrogel mask on face with firm backing paper still in place. Position correctly and carefully remove firm backing paper. Wear for 30-40 minutes. Remove mask, do not rinse. Excess serum can be applied to neck, décolletage and hands.
